## üõ°Ô∏è What Is This?
**ArcBackup‚Ñ¢** is a field-tested, culturally aware, drop-in backup ritual designed to preserve your entire Arc Browser profile (Microsoft Store Edition).

Backups are timestamped, zipped, verified, and logged to the BLACK_VAULT‚Ñ¢ like sacred digital scrolls. Arc must be safely closed to ensure full profile integrity.

