## ‚ú® Features
- ‚úÖ Microsoft Store install path auto-detection
- ‚úÖ Supports **multi-profile**, full session state, pinned tabs, extensions, boosts
- ‚úÖ Zipped archive output to **any location** (default: `Z:\THE_BLACK_VAULT\_BACKUPS`)
- ‚úÖ Logs every step to `SMART_LOGS` (default: `C:\Temple_Strike\Scripts\SMART_LOGS`)
- ‚úÖ **Safe to run after closing Arc**
- ‚úÖ Auto-cleans backups older than 30 days
- ‚úÖ No installation required ‚Äî just run the `.bat`

---

## üîß Installation
1. Clone this repo or download the `.zip`
2. Drop it anywhere safe (e.g. `C:\Temple_Strike\Scripts`)
3. Right-click > Run as Administrator (or just double-click if elevated)

---

## ‚òëÔ∏è Usage
```
ArcBrowserProfile_SolutionPlus_bkup.bat
```
- Creates a folder like:
  ```
  Z:\THE_BLACK_VAULT\_BACKUPS\ArcBackups\ArcBackup_2025-05-17_17-00-23.zip
  ```
- If Arc is open, it will notify you and pause
- If no Arc data is found, it logs the issue and aborts

